TITLE: Injecting Custom CurlMulti Object Into Clients Using Event Listener in PHP
DESCRIPTION: Code example showing how to reuse the same CurlMulti object across multiple clients by adding a listener to the ServiceBuilder's service_builder.create_client event.
SOURCE: https://github.com/guzzle/guzzle/blob/7.9/UPGRADING.md#2025-04-22_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
$multi = new Guzzle\Http\Curl\CurlMulti();
$builder = Guzzle\Service\Builder\ServiceBuilder::factory('/path/to/config.json');
$builder->addListener('service_builder.create_client', function ($event) use ($multi) {
    $event['client']->setCurlMulti($multi);
}
});
```

